{"tid":1062141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12名共和黨人倒戈，參議院通過堵截緊急狀態興建美墨圍牆","createTime":"2019-03-15T01:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T01:53:18.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35bce86837896a6b184adccd133ee4f44b7507ca","tid":1062141,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"美國參議院周四通過決議，終止總統特朗普上月中頒佈的緊急狀態令。早已揚言將以總統權力否決那項國會決議的特朗普，在表決後於Twitter發了一個詞：VETO！（否決）。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上月中宣佈全國緊急狀態，以調動款項興建美墨圍牆。民主黨掌控的眾議院上月底以245比182票通過堵截緊急狀態令，獲13名共和黨議員倒戈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參議院雖由共和黨控制，堵截緊急狀態令議案以59對41票獲通過，因有12名共和黨人倒戈。<br />\n<br />\n不過，即使議案獲兩院通過，特朗普早已明言「100%」肯定將以總統權力否決，而兩院要推翻特朗普的否決，須集合2/3票數，外界預料難度極高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190315&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59370342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190315%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59370342&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=a6437bdb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190315%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59370342&h=624d3907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190315&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59370342</a>"},{"pid":"fff3ae56d46dcb844c8bffb739ff46dbaf9c2cc3","tid":1062141,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e853d517ce3a5569ecaf82d7292cd9c46e93085","tid":1062141,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:30:54.000Z","msg":"TRUMP真係擇善固執 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805eb5ed4e9fa61d92c800e36e7e678847e0c7f1","tid":1062141,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83330b2b152cbfe92ad6